album.title: Christmas Stories and Carols Audio
album.description: A wonderfully festive collection of favourite stories and carols for the whole family to enjoy over the Christmas holidays. Take a sleigh ride to the Snow Queen's palace, a trip on a donkey to Bethlehem or sing along with Good King Wenceslas in Christmas Stories and Carols. With an approximate running time of 50 minutes, these well-known Christmas stories and carols, read and sung by popular Children's TV presenters Derek Griffiths and Katy Ashworth, will bring festive cheer to every family. Added sound effects and music will keep children listening again and again, at home or in the car. Stories: 1. The Nativity Story 2. The Nutcracker & the Mouse King 3. A Christmas Carol 4. The Snow Queen 5. The Night Before Christmas Carols: 1. Twelve Days of Christmas 2. The First Noel 3. Away in a Manger 4. Holly and the Ivy 5. Hark! The Herald Angels Sing 6. O Little Town of Bethlehem 7. Good King Wenceslas 8. Deck the Halls 9. We Three Kings 10. Silent Night 11. God Rest Ye, Merry Gentlemen 12. Jingle Bells 13. Once in Royal David's City 14. O Holy Night 15. We Wish you a Merry Christmas
